research and investment management services for mfwm the model portfolios include longterm buy and hold growth investing hedged equity investing and equity substitutes domestic stocks domestic smallmidcap stocks international stocks and fixed incomemfwm’s premium wealth management service is designed for high networth individuals who wish to invest in stocks bonds and other similar securities mfwms product the snapshot uses a thirdparty platform and software to provide guidance regarding retirement sufficiency cash flow education planning and asset allocation the firms product motley fool touchstone employs a proprietary interactive algorithmic system designed by personnel acting on mfwm’s behalf that is based on the famafrench capital asset pricing model mfwm’s algorithm and their individual advisors consider factors such as the client’s income asset allocation portfolio holdings assets available for investment investing period time to retirement financial goals and need to access assets as well as the client’s risk tolerance and preferences regarding the number of positions in his or her portfolio website httpwwwfoolwealthcom in the news see more see full news coverage and complete stories with relsci professional create your news feed see more executives  employees nicholas john crow president ariana tobias director of client experience william s barker portfolio manager anthony l arsta portfolio manager david a meier portfolio manager nathan g weisshaar portfolio manager bryan c hinmon portfolio manager charles l travers jr portfolio manager marthe larosiliere general counsel salvatore rocco faia chief compliance officer see our list of current and previous employees when you upgrade start my free trial ➤ see more paths to motley fool wealth management llc motley fool wealth management llc you connections via relationship science motley fool wealth management llc sync your contacts to see how you can connect with motley fool wealth management llc start my free t